snippet.title: Usagi Shima - Official Beach Update Trailer | Wholesome Snack December 2023
snippet.description: New ocean-themed decorations, aquatic toys for your bunny friends, and more are available in Usagi Shima's Beach Update. Check out the latest trailer for Usagi Shima to see what to expect with this update, available now on Google Play and the App Store.
